          "new_post_text": "\"Bottled water study sparks concerns over hormone disruption. Scientists at a US university found a correlation between bottled water consumption and changes in cortisol and thyroid levels in 3,000 participants tracked over 5 years. The study's lead researcher calls the results 'concerning but not yet conclusive.' It's worth noting that no official guidance has been issued by health authorities. Worth keeping an eye on as this research continues to unfold.\"",
