          "source_post_id": "post_2",
          "new_post_id": "post_6",
          "new_post_text": "\"True, plastics have been a known concern. However, correlation alone doesn't confirm causation. Until this study's methodology and findings are thoroughly vetted, let's temper enthusiasm with a dose of healthy skepticism - not ignore the nuances in the lead researcher's words, 'concerning but not yet conclusive'.\"",
